author: @Myluv.k-pop
text: Dear kpop stans, ATTENTION PLEASE I would request everyone to screen shot this and copy this using google lens and share it at every kpop vid you see. I just want a few minutes of your time. Just calm down. I request you to read this without skipping and sincerely. Nowadays as the population of kpop is increasing, the amount of hate by so called sigma, chads, football fans blah blah blah is also increasing. And what makes this situation worse is the fans reaction. Yeah!! Nowadays, as you all know how these idols are treated by the toxic internet. They call them gay, call them weak and be racist towards them. Please stop replying to the post shipping idols because imagine someone shipped you with a person you believe is you friend. Stop replying to such video's and stop making disgusting edits for fun, cuz you know what? Its not fun! You know what happened to Stray Kids when they attended the Met Gala, and what usually happens to BTS on the internet and Blackpink. I daily encounter 4-5 approx. shorts/reels hating on BTS. Like comparing them with their favourite football idols and lot more, and the comments are like, proud to be a hater, kpop hater etc. So now please, listen carefully, to stop this we first have to stop the fight among ourselves. Like btw diff kpop stans. Like we need to stop hating different groups or stop fighting like, "No bts is the best!" No, its Blackpink!" Stop it. We need to unite. Everyone we need to stop hating the groups that are not our favourite's. EVERYONE HAS THEIR FAVORITE GROUP. Next step is very important. We need to stop reacting or commenting on Kpop hate vids. Or reply any hateful comment or write any comment defending your favs. For eg. You saw an edit a guy is comparing bts with ronaldo/messi etc. and he disrespected bts in that, don't react don't comment just stop. You don't to write any comment in that post. Nor you have to reply to those shit comments, just ignore. Report that video/short/reel that's it! Simple. Please baby stans, please stop fighting everywhere. AND WRITING COMMENTS LIKE: Blackpink the best, JENNIE, KIM TAEHYUNG everywhere. Please, it's just so cringe and shows how immature you are. Stop crying everywhere" Ohh why u hate BTS" Stop creating cringe edits and FANFICTIONS. Stop giving time to these teenage boy's shitty opinions who think they are chads and sigma by hating. And at last, all kpop fans, let's make a promise we won't hate each other. Respect each other and our opinions. Stop arguing and giving time to haters. Because the more you react.
